data.text:
Charlotte of Savoy and Louis XI of France were married for 32 years before Louis XI of France died, leaving behind his partner and 11 children.

They had 11 children, Louis (565), Joachim (565), Louise (564), Anne (563), Joan (560), Louis (557), Louis (557), Charles (554), Charles (554), Francis (551) and Francis (551).
